    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当雨水不再与风同行，而是涌向室内，便成了“躲风雨”天气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一怪异天气究竟从何而来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >异常事件的调查者蘑菇收到了一个模糊的调查委托，拜托其前往一所房子调查，然而房子的主人木匠希尔洛却似乎对此并不知情。在这里，弥漫着怪异的氛围，奇怪的木头耳朵随处可见，“好像是最近才冒出来的，大概是因为下了太久的雨吧。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演蘑菇，追踪线索，解开谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《蘑菇的异常事件调查记录：躲风雨》是一款点击式奇幻冒险解谜游戏，由慢i鸹i团队制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>具体操作说明如下：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标左键：控制移动/场景交互/确认</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼠标右键：呼出菜单/取消</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/870179e40423d604e442505f43e76e52.apng?t=1744181505\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/870179e40423d604e442505f43e76e52.poster.avif?t=1744181505\" class=\"bb_img\" width=110 height=100 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时长：0.5-2小时</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>充满想象力的艺术风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坠入兔子洞，在日常幻想中开始奇妙冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/af549656b5109c25c1fe979ed4f4bdbf.avif?t=1744181505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras_big/af549656b5109c25c1fe979ed4f4bdbf.avif?t=1744181505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式的线索收集体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-可以同所有物体交互（但是要注意甄别有效线索哦！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/ba4efb2934bc1468e31a95cae8ad836e.avif?t=1744181505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras_big/ba4efb2934bc1468e31a95cae8ad836e.avif?t=1744181505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>哪怕是再基础的解谜工具，似乎也有自己的个性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/1f55b8788a0906aa57b977bfdfae745e.avif?t=1744181505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras_big/1f55b8788a0906aa57b977bfdfae745e.avif?t=1744181505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>紧扣剧情的独特谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/79dbfaed6146f7c895268f316ac2eb7d.avif?t=1744181505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras_big/79dbfaed6146f7c895268f316ac2eb7d.avif?t=1744181505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>共有三个不同结局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/7b32067bbadd3213797849c4f26ce52d.webp?t=1744181505\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/7b32067bbadd3213797849c4f26ce52d.poster.avif?t=1744181505\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=337 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三首原创音乐</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/887156e8b4d546cdf25f42b951cef54d.webp?t=1744181505\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289210/extras/887156e8b4d546cdf25f42b951cef54d.poster.avif?t=1744181505\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
